    "description": "<strong>《Steelborn》</strong>是一款以经典游戏为灵感的平台射击游戏，制作团队由 Abuse、Ranger-X、魂斗罗、合金弹头、Blaster Master 和 HERO 的资深粉丝组成。<br><br>地球总部与远在天边的 VL-744 星球拓居地失联，你将登上忠实的机甲去一探究竟。玩法引人入胜，故事跌宕起伏，绝对让你无法自拔！<br><br>登上强大的战斗机甲去探索游戏世界，离开机甲又能深入星球上的无人秘境。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786930/extras/91ddc21925b2b9d1a129de7ce171ea85.poster.avif?t=1678250938\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786930/extras/91ddc21925b2b9d1a129de7ce171ea85.webm?t=1678250938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786930/extras/91ddc21925b2b9d1a129de7ce171ea85.mp4?t=1678250938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>武器多样：一共五种，推进背包、等离子炮、还有武士刀！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786930/extras/3004c6689fd131c8b2c87aafcdc9188d.poster.avif?t=1678250938\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786930/extras/3004c6689fd131c8b2c87aafcdc9188d.webm?t=1678250938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786930/extras/3004c6689fd131c8b2c87aafcdc9188d.mp4?t=1678250938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>战胜各种敌人和危险的首领<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786930/extras/99f1d9b3f3adb9cec136c2292fd641be.poster.avif?t=1678250938\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786930/extras/99f1d9b3f3adb9cec136c2292fd641be.webm?t=1678250938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shar